{"tid":2072472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛(梁國雄) 隻過街老鼠上屆差d輸比哪吒包尾入都重敢出黎選？好心佢咪咁戀權退落黎交棒啦","createTime":"2020-06-20T15:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T13:00:46.000Z","uid":252492,"like":13,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8d12b004805ef8996774202a6d4b3d3bbf39a5","tid":2072472,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上屆都新東尾席 臨尾重新點票點左幾次 先僅僅贏方國珊千幾票, 今年仲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個黨又過街老鼠 果陣就屌選民話唔希罕後生仔既票<br />\n上次都差d選唔到咁濟 好心就退落黎交棒比姓岑果個啦 起碼形象無佢同個黨咁撚差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Me7P4i9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMe7P4i9.png&h=dee90d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb3ca7dbf286e89bde65bc5c03395e0162aa5ba","tid":2072472,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民政治明星是不能屌的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>佢明條毛咩 上次點幾次票先包尾入最尾果席"},{"pid":"454a2e62e34f2354e5d09791850ba01cf1ce9b05","tid":2072472,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果區會由王喜挑琼子，應該贏撚左<br />\n<br />\n長毛個定位係中產又唔BUY、後生又唔BUY</blockquote>加上果陣屌鳩後生得罪哂本土派咁濟<br />\n再加上佢近幾年攪鳩本土派同佢地兩登既過街老鼠形象<br />\n呃連登班唔知佢地以前衰野既政治新手就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7023007c4c3d8542efb19329b06fb9d3092fce9d","tid":2072472,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0eb3ca7dbf286e89bde65bc5c03395e0162aa5ba","tid":2072472,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民政治明星是不能屌的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>佢明條毛咩 上次點幾次票先包尾入最尾果席"},"citedBy":0,"repl